This paper is about improving recommender systems, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. The paper also discusses the issue of popularity bias, which is a common problem in machine learning (cs.LG) and the proposed approach involves weighting items, which is a technique used in information filtering (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper mentions using existing recommendation algorithms, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and the paper discusses the potential benefits for businesses, which could fall under the cybernetics (cs.CY) sub-category.
